title: Hawkeye Miniseries
description:
Hawkeye (Clint Barton), also known as Ronin is a fictional character that appears in the comic books published by Marvel Comics. The character first appeared in Tales of Suspense #57 (vol. 1, Sept. 1964) and was created by writer Stan Lee and artist Don Heck.

This torrent contains 2 Miniseries of Hawkeye. one published in 1983 and other in 2003/04. Another miniseries of Hawkeye was published in 1993-94, but its not posted because I dont have it. And if anyone of you has it, then feel free to post it.

Enjoy and Seed.
